{"tid":2147874,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港幣與美元脫鉤，與人民幣進行掛鉤。","createTime":"2020-08-09T14:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T07:00:29.000Z","uid":70964,"like":193,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"71cfd5c36f87de5f76aedc2be80ca69adb4f8a63","tid":2147874,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:01:08.000Z","msg":"任志剛曾在 1997、1998 年帶領香港走出亞洲金融風暴、並擊退索羅斯等國際炒家，維持住香港的聯繫匯率制度和金融穩定。<br />\n<br />\n一：港幣與美元脫鉤，與人民幣進行掛鉤。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">任志剛在該份研究報告中提出港府或許應考慮脫鉤美元，轉而掛鉤人民幣的想法，當時任志剛此一倡議震撼了全香港金融圈，但隨後遭香港特首梁振英否決。</span><br />\n<br />\n而以目前的狀況來看，澳盛銀行 (ANZ) 經濟學家 Raymond Yeung 認為，香港脫鉤美元在未來 5 至 10 年內都不太可能發生，因為人民幣雖然納入了國際貨幣基金組織 (IMF) 的特別提款權 (SDR) 之內，但它還需要一些時間才能成為穩定的儲備貨幣。"},{"pid":"4a66b37b0895b591164f0a661b3885576891b619","tid":2147874,"uid":38904,"like":121,"dislike":2,"score":119,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:03:00.000Z","msg":"但係人民幣同美債掛鉤喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c2eb923494878a9f672fd41ae7ccda4afda62c","tid":2147874,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:04:21.000Z","msg":"加速"},{"pid":"5bd2594d0d39d0a6eb58b5801a8e85d63a4118b7","tid":2147874,"uid":70964,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:04:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人訪問下林奠會唔會實行"},{"pid":"aeefa4c5990e387c7f915cde310acaa977803f43","tid":2147874,"uid":70964,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"4a66b37b0895b591164f0a661b3885576891b619","tid":2147874,"uid":38904,"like":121,"dislike":2,"score":119,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:03:00.000Z","msg":"但係人民幣同美債掛鉤喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:05:23.000Z","msg":"林奠仲唔撚到鎂了"},{"pid":"3c87e2d279f5285da4b8a78d369a9adcd0995b86","tid":2147874,"uid":38778,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:06:58.000Z","msg":"仲有港幣？ 你係咪港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\